 s←SetCorner(s corners ci w h halfAngle);sweepRange
⍝ Set target corner and compute sweep parameters
 ⎕IO←0
 s.corner←corners[ci;]
 s.inward←(180÷○1)×12○(0J1×(w÷2)-⊃s.corner)+(h÷2)-1⊃s.corner
 s.sweep←0
 ⍝ Sweep ±90° from inward to cover both walls at the corner
 sweepRange←90-halfAngle
 s.sweepDir←{⍵≤0:3 ⋄ 3}sweepRange
 s.sweepMax←45⌈sweepRange
